cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U to 0 will cause invalid GTP-U port configuration and prevent S1-U interface setup.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U 設定為 0 會導致無效的 GTP-U 端口配置，並阻止 S1-U 接口設置。

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_dl with upper bound less than lower bound will cause timing misalignment and prevent proper front-haul synchronization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_cp_dl 的上限設定為小於下限會導致時序錯位，並阻止正確的前傳同步。
